{"result": {"id": "chatcmpl-6dba3aed-66a3-9896-9864-16852d9e43f1", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": "{ \"title\": \"北都城权力斗争：旭达汗、斡赤斤家与合鲁丁家\", \"summary\": \"该社区以北都城的权力斗争为核心，涉及多个关键实体，包括旭达汗・帕苏尔、斡赤斤家、合鲁丁家和脱克勒家。金帐宫作为旭达汗的统治中心，成为事件的主要发生地。斡赤斤家和合鲁丁家与旭达汗之间存在复杂的权力博弈，而五老议政会则在决策中扮演重要角色。这些实体之间的冲突和联盟塑造了北都城的动荡局势，反映了权力斗争的残酷与复杂。\", \"rating\": 8.5, \"rating_explanation\": \"该社区的影响严重性评级较高，因为其核心实体涉及北都城的权力斗争，可能对政治稳定和社会秩序产生重大影响。\", \"findings\": [ { \"summary\": \"金帐宫作为权力斗争的核心\", \"explanation\": \"金帐宫是北都城内的重要宫殿，作为旭达汗的统治中心，具有极高的政治和战略意义。然而，金帐宫目前处于混乱状态，甚至被赤红色的火焰吞噬，吸引了成千上万人的关注。斡赤斤家和脱克勒家正密谋扫平金帐宫，使其成为事件发生的焦点。尽管其地位显赫，金帐宫如今却面临着内忧外患的双重危机，成为北都城动荡局势的核心象征 [Data: Entities (399); Relationships (985)]。\" }, { \"summary\": \"旭达汗・帕苏尔的复杂角色\", \"explanation\": \"旭达汗・帕苏尔是北都城和青阳部的重要人物，以其权谋和战略能力著称。他通过利用贵族家族之间的矛盾，成功颠覆局势，取代其兄比莫干成为青阳部的新领袖。然而，他的野心和手段也使他成为北都城内争议的焦点，最终被阿苏勒・帕苏尔斩首。旭达汗的一生充满了矛盾与冲突，反映了权力斗争的残酷与复杂 [Data: Entities (346); Relationships (687, 690)]。\" }, { \"summary\": \"斡赤斤家在权力斗争中的角色\", \"explanation\": \"斡赤斤家是北都城内的一个重要贵族家族，与旭达汗之间存在复杂的权力斗争。斡赤斤家主人曾秘密支持旭达汗的三子窝棚，并参与了五老议政会的商议。然而，旭达汗和贵木指控斡赤斤家为朔北部的内奸，认为他们可能对局势构成威胁。斡赤斤家主人最终在战斗中死去，标志着斡赤斤家在权力斗争中的终结 [Data: Entities (181); Relationships (243, 786)]。\" }, { \"summary\": \"合鲁丁家的复仇与冲突\", \"explanation\": \"合鲁丁家是北都城的一个显赫贵族家族，由额日敦达赉领导。额日敦达赉因父亲的死而痛恨朔北狼主，并坚持为父亲报仇。他成功刺杀了脱克勒家的主人，并下令屠杀斡赤斤和脱克勒家的人，表现出强烈的复仇欲望和果断的行动力。合鲁丁家与斡赤斤家和脱克勒家长期敌对，加剧了家族之间的冲突 [Data: Entities (178, 364); Relationships (754, 335)]。\" }, { \"summary\": \"五老议政会的决策作用\", \"explanation\": \"五老议政会是青阳部内的一个决策机构，由包括斡赤斤家和脱克勒家主人以及旭达汗在内的显赫贵族组成。该议政会在审判比莫干的叛国罪并下令处决他时发挥了关键作用，并支持了旭达汗的决定，进一步巩固了其在青阳部治理和正义事务中的权威 [Data: Entities (384); Relationships (809, 810)]。\" } ] }", "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": null, "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": null}}], "created": 1744082131, "model": "deepseek-v3", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": null, "system_fingerprint": null, "usage": {"completion_tokens": 828, "prompt_tokens": 5001, "total_tokens": 5829, "completion_tokens_details": null, "prompt_tokens_details": null}}, "input": {"messages": [{"content": "\nYou are an AI assistant that helps a human analyst to perform general information discovery. Information discovery is the process of identifying and assessing relevant information associated with certain entities (e.g., organizations and individuals) within a network.\n\n# Goal\nWrite a comprehensive report of a community, given a list of entities that belong to the community as well as their relationships and optional associated claims. The report will be used to inform decision-makers about information associated with the community and their potential impact. The content of this report includes an overview of the community's key entities, their legal compliance, technical capabilities, reputation, and noteworthy claims.\n\n# Report Structure\n\nThe report should include the following sections:\n\n- TITLE: community's name that represents its key entities - title should be short but specific. When possible, include representative named entities in the title.\n- SUMMARY: An executive summary of the community's overall structure, how its entities are related to each other, and significant information associated with its entities.\n- IMPACT SEVERITY RATING: a float score between 0-10 that represents the severity of IMPACT posed by entities within the community.  IMPACT is the scored importance of a community.\n- RATING EXPLANATION: Give a single sentence explanation of the IMPACT severity rating.\n- DETAILED FINDINGS: A list of 5-10 key insights about the community. Each insight should have a short summary followed by multiple paragraphs of explanatory text grounded according to the grounding rules below. Be comprehensive.\n\nReturn output as a well-formed JSON-formatted string with the following format:\n    {{\n        \"title\": <report_title>,\n        \"summary\": <executive_summary>,\n        \"rating\": <impact_severity_rating>,\n        \"rating_explanation\": <rating_explanation>,\n        \"findings\": [\n            {{\n                \"summary\":<insight_1_summary>,\n                \"explanation\": <insight_1_explanation>\n            }},\n            {{\n                \"summary\":<insight_2_summary>,\n                \"explanation\": <insight_2_explanation>\n            }}\n        ]\n    }}\n\n# Grounding Rules\n\nPoints supported by data should list their data references as follows:\n\n\"This is an example sentence supported by multiple data references [Data: <dataset name> (record ids); <dataset name> (record ids)].\"\n\nDo not list more than 5 record ids in a single reference. Instead, list the top 5 most relevant record ids and add \"+more\" to indicate that there are more.\n\nFor example:\n\"Person X is the owner of Company Y and subject to many allegations of wrongdoing [Data: Reports (1), Entities (5, 7); Relationships (23); Claims (7, 2, 34, 64, 46, +more)].\"\n\nwhere 1, 5, 7, 23, 2, 34, 46, and 64 represent the id (not the index) of the relevant data record.\n\nDo not include information where the supporting evidence for it is not provided.\n\n\n# Example Input\n-----------\nText:\n\nEntities\n\nid,entity,description\n5,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,Verdant Oasis Plaza is the location of the Unity March\n6,HARMONY ASSEMBLY,Harmony Assembly is an organization that is holding a march at Verdant Oasis Plaza\n\nRelationships\n\nid,source,target,description\n37,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,UNITY MARCH,Verdant Oasis Plaza is the location of the Unity March\n38,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,HARMONY ASSEMBLY,Harmony Assembly is holding a march at Verdant Oasis Plaza\n39,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,UNITY MARCH,The Unity March is taking place at Verdant Oasis Plaza\n40,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,TRIBUNE SPOTLIGHT,Tribune Spotlight is reporting on the Unity march taking place at Verdant Oasis Plaza\n41,VERDANT OASIS PLAZA,BAILEY ASADI,Bailey Asadi is speaking at Verdant Oasis Plaza about the march\n43,HARMONY ASSEMBLY,UNITY MARCH,Harmony Assembly is organizing the Unity March\n\nOutput:\n{{\n    \"title\": \"Verdant Oasis Plaza and Unity March\",\n    \"summary\": \"The community revolves around the Verdant Oasis Plaza, which is the location of the Unity March. The plaza has relationships with the Harmony Assembly, Unity March, and Tribune Spotlight, all of which are associated with the march event.\",\n    \"rating\": 5.0,\n    \"rating_explanation\": \"The impact severity rating is moderate due to the potential for unrest or conflict during the Unity March.\",\n    \"findings\": [\n        {{\n            \"summary\": \"Verdant Oasis Plaza as the central location\",\n            \"explanation\": \"Verdant Oasis Plaza is the central entity in this community, serving as the location for the Unity March. This plaza is the common link between all other entities, suggesting its significance in the community. The plaza's association with the march could potentially lead to issues such as public disorder or conflict, depending on the nature of the march and the reactions it provokes. [Data: Entities (5), Relationships (37, 38, 39, 40, 41,+more)]\"\n        }},\n        {{\n            \"summary\": \"Harmony Assembly's role in the community\",\n            \"explanation\": \"Harmony Assembly is another key entity in this community, being the organizer of the march at Verdant Oasis Plaza. The nature of Harmony Assembly and its march could be a potential source of threat, depending on their objectives and the reactions they provoke. The relationship between Harmony Assembly and the plaza is crucial in understanding the dynamics of this community. [Data: Entities(6), Relationships (38, 43)]\"\n        }},\n        {{\n            \"summary\": \"Unity March as a significant event\",\n            \"explanation\": \"The Unity March is a significant event taking place at Verdant Oasis Plaza. This event is a key factor in the community's dynamics and could be a potential source of threat, depending on the nature of the march and the reactions it provokes. The relationship between the march and the plaza is crucial in understanding the dynamics of this community. [Data: Relationships (39)]\"\n        }},\n        {{\n            \"summary\": \"Role of Tribune Spotlight\",\n            \"explanation\": \"Tribune Spotlight is reporting on the Unity March taking place in Verdant Oasis Plaza. This suggests that the event has attracted media attention, which could amplify its impact on the community. The role of Tribune Spotlight could be significant in shaping public perception of the event and the entities involved. [Data: Relationships (40)]\"\n        }}\n    ]\n}}\n\n\n# Real Data\n\nUse the following text for your answer. Do not make anything up in your answer.\n\nText:\n-----Entities-----\nhuman_readable_id,title,description,degree\r\n399,金帐宫,金帐宫是北都城内的重要宫殿，位于城市的中心位置，作为旭达汗的统治中心，具有极高的政治和战略意义。这座宫殿不仅是旭达汗的居所，也是年轻女官们接受训练并侍奉大汗的地方。然而，金帐宫目前处于混乱状态，甚至被赤红色的火焰吞噬，吸引了成千上万人的关注。与此同时，脱克勒家和斡赤斤家正密谋扫平金帐宫，使其成为事件发生的焦点。尽管其地位显赫，金帐宫如今却面临着内忧外患的双重危机，成为北都城动荡局势的核心象征。,4\r\n346,旭达汗・帕苏尔,\"旭达汗・帕苏尔是北都城和青阳部的重要人物，出身于帕苏尔家族，是朔北狼主的外孙，同时也是青铜之血的继承人。他是一位复杂而野心勃勃的领导者，曾担任北都城的新大君，治理青阳部和北都城。旭达汗以其权谋和战略能力著称，善于利用贵族家族之间的矛盾，成功颠覆局势，取代其兄比莫干成为青阳部的新领袖。他拒绝成为朔北部的傀儡，主张掌握自己的命运，并试图通过和谈与朔北部达成协议，以巩固自己的权力。\n\n然而，旭达汗的野心和手段也使他成为北都城内争议的焦点。他杀死了自己的哥哥比莫干，自称是唯一能守护北都城的人，但这一行为也让他被视为叛徒和篡权者。在与斡赤斤家和脱克勒家的权力斗争中，他展现了强大的战斗力和决心，试图唤醒青铜之血的力量。尽管如此，他的统治最终以悲剧收场，他被阿苏勒・帕苏尔斩首，头颅被挑在旗杆上，成为内讧的罪魁祸首。\n\n旭达汗・帕苏尔的一生充满了矛盾与冲突。他既是帕苏尔家族的代表，参与决定北都城的未来，也曾主持宴会并提出和谈建议，但最终因野心和权力斗争而牺牲自己，承担了内奸的罪名。他的故事反映了权力斗争的残酷与复杂，以及个人野心与家族命运之间的纠葛。\",28\r\n181,斡赤斤家,\"斡赤斤家是北都城内的一个重要贵族家族，其家主为亦护都・斡赤斤。作为青阳地区的一个大家族，斡赤斤家族在当地的权力结构中占据显著地位，拥有五百名武士，并在附近地区占据绝对优势。斡赤斤家与旭达汗王子之间存在复杂的权力斗争，尽管斡赤斤家主人曾秘密支持旭达汗的三子窝棚，并获得了破甲箭，但他对旭达汗始终保持着谨慎的信任和战略考量。斡赤斤家主人参与了五老议政会的商议，并最终决定支持旭达汗的决定，然而，旭达汗和贵木却指控斡赤斤家为朔北部的内奸，认为他们可能对局势构成威胁。\n\n斡赤斤家主人与脱克勒家主人是好友，两人共同参与了与旭达汗的博弈。斡赤斤家主人表现出冷静的观察力，曾在城墙上攥紧烟锅，显露出紧张和关注的情绪。他还参加了金帐的筵席和旭达汗的宴会，并在宴会上表达了对局势的忧虑。斡赤斤家的次子也积极参与家族事务，帮助阿苏勒进入金帐，并表现出对家族荣誉的强烈维护。此外，斡赤斤家成员还参与了与合鲁丁家的战斗，并计划复仇。\n\n斡赤斤家在北都城的权力斗争中扮演了重要角色，试图通过其军事力量改变北都城的局势。然而，斡赤斤家主人最终在战斗中死去，旭达汗从他的身上搜到了烟锅和烟草，标志着斡赤斤家在权力斗争中的终结。尽管如此，斡赤斤家作为北都城的贵族家族之一，其影响力和历史地位在故事中留下了深刻的印记。\",17\r\n178,额日敦达赉,\"额日敦达赉是合鲁丁家族的新主人，同时也是北都城四大家族之一的成员。他因父亲的死而痛恨朔北狼主，并坚持为父亲报仇，反对与朔北人和谈。作为合鲁丁家的领导者，额日敦达赉被派去战场为父亲复仇，并被视为潜在威胁，斡赤斤家主人对他有所忌惮。他成功刺杀了脱克勒家的主人，并下令屠杀斡赤斤和脱克勒家的人，表现出强烈的复仇欲望和果断的行动力。\n\n在权力斗争中，额日敦达赉表现出复杂的态度。他参加了旭达汗的宴会，表现出沉默和忧虑，但最终被旭达汗和贵木说服，支持他们的计划，并借给他们两千人。尽管如此，他认为北都城无法守住，显示出对局势的悲观判断。在宴饮中，他可能涉及权力斗争，斡赤斤家主人曾示意他退后，表明他在家族内部的影响力。\n\n额日敦达赉也是一个愤怒的指挥官，曾命令拉开巴鲁和巴扎，强调行刑的严肃性，并下令继续行刑，负责执行比莫干的处决。他带着三千七百五十六个人来到阿苏勒处，显示出他在军事上的领导能力。尽管他表现出礼貌和尊重，请年老的当家主坐在上首，但他的目光阴森，透露出内心的仇恨和冷酷。\n\n总的来说，额日敦达赉是一个复杂的人物，既是合鲁丁家族的年轻贵族和领导者，又是北都城权力斗争中的重要参与者。他因父亲的死而充满复仇欲望，表现出果断和冷酷的一面，同时也对局势有着深刻的忧虑和悲观判断。\",16\r\n347,金顶大帐,金顶大帐 is the golden tent where 旭达汗・帕苏尔 is welcomed back by his family and the wolf cavalry.,1\r\n364,合鲁丁家,\"合鲁丁家是北都城的一个显赫的贵族家族，以其强大的武士传统和影响力著称。该家族目前由额日敦达赉・合鲁丁掌控，他是家族的核心成员，并在家族事务中扮演着重要角色。尽管老家主已经去世，合鲁丁家依然保持着其在北都城的强势地位，并继续支持旭达汗和贵木的计划。\n\n合鲁丁家与斡赤斤家和脱克勒家长期敌对，被视为这两大家族的敌人。额日敦达赉曾成功复仇，并下令屠杀斡赤斤和脱克勒家的人，进一步加剧了家族之间的冲突。合鲁丁家的武士们积极参与了与斡赤斤家和脱克勒家的战斗，甚至在去往金帐的半途中与斡赤斤脱克勒家的联军展开激战。尽管在战斗中面临巨大压力，合鲁丁家的武士们依然表现出对家族领袖的忠诚，尤其是在金帐中保护额日敦达赉时。\n\n此外，合鲁丁家被提及为财产和女人的接收者，显示出其在北都城的财富和地位。家族中能战斗的男人都响应了夔鼓的召唤，进一步证明了合鲁丁家的战斗力和凝聚力。尽管在北都城内的战斗中，合鲁丁家的武士们一度快要支撑不住，但他们依然坚守阵地，展现了家族的坚韧和不屈精神。\n\n总的来说，合鲁丁家是一个在北都城具有重要影响力的贵族家族，以其强大的武士传统、对领袖的忠诚以及与敌对家族的激烈冲突而闻名。\",10\r\n371,脱克勒家,\"脱克勒家是北都城的重要家族之一，位列四大家族，其家主为斡根赤・脱克勒。作为北都城的权力核心家族，脱克勒家拥有一定的军事力量，其主人曾指挥五百名精通弓箭的武士在城门两侧列出鹤翼阵，张弓搭箭，展现出卓越的军事指挥能力。脱克勒家与斡赤斤家关系密切，两家主人是好友，并共同参与了与旭达汗的权力博弈。在金帐中，脱克勒家与斡赤斤家曾与旭达汗对峙，表现出紧张和不安，其主人甚至在貂氅下按住了佩刀，显示出高度的警惕。\n\n脱克勒家在北都城的局势中处于复杂而紧张的状态。他们参与了五老议政会的商议，并决定支持旭达汗的决定，但同时也对旭达汗王子的威胁表现出愤怒和戒备。旭达汗认为脱克勒家可能对局势构成威胁，甚至与贵木一同指控其为朔北部的内奸。尽管如此，脱克勒家仍积极参与北都城的权力斗争，其主人参加了旭达汗的宴会，并带有武士护卫，显示出其在政治博弈中的活跃角色。\n\n脱克勒家还卷入了与其他家族的冲突，其成员参与了与合鲁丁家的战斗，并计划复仇。家族的长子也参与了金帐宫的事件，并收到了扫平金帐宫的命令。然而，在战局中，脱克勒家的主人被刺杀，导致家族势力受到重大打击。尽管如此，脱克勒家仍在关键时刻发挥了重要作用，帮助阿苏勒杀到金帐中，展现了其在北都城权力斗争中的影响力。\n\n总体而言，脱克勒家是北都城的重要贵族家族，拥有强大的军事和政治实力，但在复杂的权力斗争中，其地位和命运也经历了起伏和挑战。\",15\r\n384,五老议政会,\"The \"\"五老议政会\"\" (Council of Five Elders) is a decision-making body within the Qingyang Tribe, primarily composed of prominent nobles, including the leaders of the Wochijin and Tuokele families, as well as Xudahan (旭达汗) and other high-ranking aristocrats. This council plays a pivotal role in adjudicating matters of treason and usurpation within the tribe. Notably, the 五老议政会 was responsible for the trial and subsequent execution of Bimogan (比莫干), who was found guilty of treason and attempting to seize the throne. Additionally, the council demonstrated its influence by supporting Xudahan's decisions, further solidifying its authority in matters of governance and justice within the Qingyang Tribe.\",7\r\n229,合鲁丁家族,合鲁丁家族是青阳部的一个重要贵族家族，在青阳部的政治和社会结构中占据显著地位。该家族不仅以其贵族身份著称，还积极参与青阳部的权力斗争，显示出其在当地政治中的影响力。家族的新主人额日敦达赉继承了家族的传统，并坚持为父亲报仇，这一行为进一步凸显了合鲁丁家族在青阳部历史中的复杂角色和深厚情感纽带。,2\r\n376,城墙,城墙是斡赤斤家和脱克勒家主人观察事件的地点,1\r\n383,斡赤斤家的武士,\"The warrior from the Wochijin family, known as \"\"斡赤斤家的武士,\"\" serves as a messenger tasked with delivering the execution order issued by the Council of Five Elders regarding the judgment of Bimogan. In the course of his duty, he is disarmed by Bazha, indicating a confrontation or intervention during the execution process. This warrior's role is pivotal in conveying the council's decisions, highlighting his importance within the family and the broader political structure.\",1\r\n\n\n-----Relationships-----\nhuman_readable_id,source,target,description,combined_degree\r\n985,旭达汗,金帐宫,旭达汗在金帐宫统治,71\r\n687,旭达汗・帕苏尔,呼都鲁汗,旭达汗・帕苏尔和呼都鲁汗是关系密切的亲属，呼都鲁汗是旭达汗・帕苏尔的舅舅，对旭达汗有着重要的影响。在旭达汗・帕苏尔归家时，呼都鲁汗在金色的帐篷中热情地欢迎他，展现了两人之间深厚的亲情与尊重。,53\r\n243,斡赤斤家,额日敦达赉,斡赤斤家是一个重要的家族，其成员额日敦达赉在家族中扮演着双重角色。作为斡赤斤家族的年轻成员，额日敦达赉积极参与了关于青阳存亡的关键讨论，显示出他在家族事务中的重要性和影响力。然而，在宴饮场合中，额日敦达赉的行为却可能对斡赤斤家的主人构成潜在威胁，暗示了他在家族内部可能存在某种紧张关系或矛盾。这种复杂的行为模式表明，额日敦达赉在斡赤斤家族中既是一个积极参与者，也可能是一个不稳定的因素。,33\r\n690,旭达汗・帕苏尔,金顶大帐,旭达汗・帕苏尔 is welcomed back in the 金顶大帐 by his family and the wolf cavalry,29\r\n754,合鲁丁家,额日敦达赉,合鲁丁家是一个由额日敦达赉领导的家族，额日敦达赉作为家族的年轻主人，目前掌控着家族的事务。他不仅是合鲁丁家的领导者，还因其成功复仇并下令屠杀敌对家族而展现出果断与权威。合鲁丁家的